{"tid":1668563,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔡英文反問誰政治凌架法律　不點名批評香港應管的不管","createTime":"2019-10-22T05:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T06:53:43.000Z","uid":200758,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0052cd1e02a2216bf48d76f804f3cc5127dec1e5","tid":1668563,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:10:13.000Z","msg":"在台灣，蔡英文總統說台灣殺人案，雖然案發在台灣，但加害人及受害人都是香港人，香港很自然有管轄權及可作司法追溯及審批，她認為香港在這段時間放棄對公民的管轄權，對司法追溯採取不管的態度，令香港公民不能得到司法的伸張。蔡英文強調台方願意負責任亦有作準備，並無排除台方的管轄權，但必須要香港政府提供協助，否則台灣的司法機構在辦理及審判過程中，無法取得完整的資訊和證據。蔡英文反問，是誰政治凌架法律很清楚，她不點名批評香港應管的不管，認為後續事宜會由行政院處理，形容今次是司法管轄權和司法正義實施的問題，以及是否負責任政府的問題。<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-22 13:03:10<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487607-20191022.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487607-20191022.htm&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e22d0809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487607-20191022.htm&h=ff23bca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487607-20191022.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7a1111e102cab3f0d1c5cb41b46ce2498659f6fd","tid":1668563,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e1a0ff9f6631d40d2694173e9710ba3984d5a4c","tid":1668563,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:27:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">想贏同我入嚟<br />\n想connect全世界同我入嚟<br />\n把握時機 食住個勢</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"600e7ddae37d680721f4f1a0780a86f20f9a4584","tid":1668563,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eebef4462d36dbb6cb2ede55b1215f05a07c527","tid":1668563,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:37:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032e54f98a4e13f9822a72bb996e56d4617fc2e4","tid":1668563,"uid":8880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"大大聲屌柒港共就啱<br />\n仆街港共日日講壞歪理以為冇人理<br />\n上撚到國際層面 睇你點撚頂"},{"pid":"ef5f2aecc45989f4b1cdd5157a1f9f7a26b5ac81","tid":1668563,"uid":200758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"032e54f98a4e13f9822a72bb996e56d4617fc2e4","tid":1668563,"uid":8880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:43:33.000Z","msg":"大大聲屌柒港共就啱<br />\n仆街港共日日講壞歪理以為冇人理<br />\n上撚到國際層面 睇你點撚頂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"依家日日比台灣屌 睇到心都涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c755914aeec288b5a826240f230cb1aaf6cc29e3","tid":1668563,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"李家超俾english 直屌應管的不管"},{"pid":"c057aabc2543a8ea9eb3d62e42d1cd9f4b2c1935","tid":1668563,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c755914aeec288b5a826240f230cb1aaf6cc29e3","tid":1668563,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"李家超俾english 直屌應管的不管"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9471d53ccf03108739ee3b6837edd5b062e7f7cf","tid":1668563,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:09:42.000Z","msg":"蔡媽媽發言 幾乎唔睇內文都比正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a03e9a4dfc34061a32b28fc2dfe8d52d1518db0","tid":1668563,"uid":200758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:15:12.000Z","msg":"蔡英文批港府放棄公民管轄權令正義無法伸張<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在台灣，蔡英文總統表示，陳同佳案件涉及的當事人都是香港公民，批港府放棄對公民行使管轄權，讓正義無法得到伸張。<br />\n<br />\n蔡英文：「香港政府是一個很相關政府，她放棄了自己公民的管轄權，我們現在看這個案件內，雖然犯罪的發生地在台灣，可是當事人，不論加害人或被害人，都是香港公民，相關的事證都在香港，香港政府拒絕行使管轄權，讓那個受害的香港公民沒有得到正義的伸張，對於司法的追訴都採取不管的態度。這件事情誰政治凌駕法律是很清楚，應該管的不管，但我們台灣政府願意負擔這個責任。」"},{"pid":"795778d86300c5bcd0ed2f6bd7ae398b1524dd06","tid":1668563,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"港共將單case玩弄政治 在先"},{"pid":"e7d9b0cc0ffa64afd0b69e53bdbf73a3d75cbdeb","tid":1668563,"uid":131121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"蔡英文真心為台灣算係咁，台灣人仲唔知足投個發大財或者立場曚糊嘅柯P捉蟲仲死"},{"pid":"d442b8513b731b69844d3850fc7f35d65ea4340b","tid":1668563,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342619975de995d28447c4bd16ad72c4d1a24d5e","tid":1668563,"uid":34616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"小英<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9becc03edf999d9a036a4058750bf2f9e50106","tid":1668563,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"直線抽擊"},{"pid":"364e1cf8ad371a85a805331de79e4623d0557e90","tid":1668563,"uid":42978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"英文姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fbb1d01580ebdebfd25e32ac211965ac13d9ed","tid":1668563,"uid":197477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:47:22.000Z","msg":"四個月前又呢樣又果樣<br />\n依家搞唔掂就想就咁掉個人俾台灣<br />\n俾我都唔幫你食呢隻死貓啦<img src=\"/assets/